snippet.title: The Talos Principle 2 - Road to Elysium Trailer | PS5 Games
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/the-talos-principle-2/

Road to Elysium is a three-part coda that allows you to dive deeper into the world of The Talos Principle 2, reunite with beloved characters, and put your puzzle-solving skills to the test through a series of thought-provoking new stories in this expansion coming out June 14th!

Following the events of The Talos Principle 2, Road to Elysium continues the evolution of the robot world, providing you with a new perspective on some of the key moments from 1k’s journey, and challenging you in new ways with puzzles built around familiar mechanics.

#ps5 #ps5games #talosprinciple2
